         <h1>
          Join American Atheists
         </h1>
         <p>
          For more than 50 years, American Atheists has been fighting to protect the absolute separation of religion from government and the civil rights of atheists. We rely on the generosity and support of our members to make our work possible. Your voice is just as important as your financial gift. By becoming a member of American Atheists, you are demonstrating that you support our work and demand full equality from your government.
         </p>
         <p>
          Without you, American Atheists would not be what it is today: the most vocal advocate for reason, rationality, and the separation of religion from government in the United States.
          <strong>
           Please join American Atheists today and help us fight for our rights.
          </strong>
         </p>
         <p>
          All membership levels include a membership card, access to the online version of our quarterly magazine, and a bi-monthly members-only newsletter.
         </p>
         <p>
          <em>
           <span style="font-size: 8pt;">
            Contributions to American Atheists are tax deductible.
            <a href="http://atheists.org/donate/tax-information">
             To learn more, click here.
            </a>
           </span>
          </em>
         </p>
         <p>
         </p>
